## Verification Plan

### Phase 1 Verification

#### Build & Lint
- `npm run build` — Ensure zero build errors
- `npm run lint` — Ensure zero lint warnings

#### Visual Verification
- Launch dev server and screenshot every page/section
- Test responsive layouts at 320px, 768px, 1024px, 1440px
- Verify all animations play smoothly

#### SEO Verification
- Check all pages have proper `<title>`, `<meta description>`, `<h1>`
- Verify JSON-LD schema renders correctly
- Check all images have alt text

#### Accessibility
- Verify keyboard navigation works on all interactive elements
- Check color contrast ratios meet WCAG AA
- Test with screen reader announcements for key CTAs

#### Performance
- Check Lighthouse score targets: Performance > 90, Accessibility > 90, SEO > 95

